OL,3,CThe far-reaching impact of Plymouth's
OL,4,C'unsafe building' crisis
OL,6,FA single crack in a concrete beam is
OL,7,Fhaving far-reaching consequences in a
OL,8,Fquiet corner of Plymouth.
OL,10,FEvolution Cove, an unassuming
OL,11,Fapartment complex built 16 years ago
OL,12,Fin Durnford Street, Stonehouse, has
OL,13,Fbeen in the spotlight for all the
OL,14,Fwrong reasons over the past four weeks.
OL,16,FHow much longer the crisis will last
OL,17,Fis anyone's guess. The more time
OL,18,Fpasses, the more the disruption spills
OL,19,Fout across the city, impacting more
OL,20,Fand more lives.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/12
