PN,43303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F433A1776946268
OL,3,CThe far-reaching impact of Plymouth's
OL,4,C'unsafe building' crisis
OL,6,FThey stood on the pavement outside,
OL,7,Fsome in pyjamas and dressing gowns,
OL,8,Fand were told to pack their bags as
OL,9,Fthe building was 'unstable' and at
OL,10,Frisk of collapse.
OL,12,FMany of them were put up in hotels,
OL,13,Fthen moved to apartments or bedsits
OL,14,Fand told to await further instructions.
OL,16,FTheir expenses are being paid by
OL,17,FCentrick, the building management
OL,18,Fcompany. But patience is wearing thin,
OL,19,Fand some say it it causing them
OL,20,Fanxiety.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/12
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
