PN,43305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F433A1776946268
OL,3,CThe far-reaching impact of Plymouth's
OL,4,C'unsafe building' crisis
OL,6,FDave is unable to go back inside to
OL,7,Fretrieve personal belongings, so is
OL,8,Fbeing forced to buy new supplies as
OL,9,FEden continues to grow.
OL,11,FJon Dingle is staying in a guesthouse
OL,12,Fin Keyham and parenting his 20-year-
OL,13,Fold son, who is has autism. Change and
OL,14,Fdisruption is difficult and unsettling
OL,15,Ffor many people and is often more so
OL,16,Ffor those who are neurodivergent.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/12
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
