CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F433A1776946268
OL,3,CThe far-reaching impact of Plymouth's
OL,4,C'unsafe building' crisis
OL,6,FSusanna Triki and her pet cockatiel
OL,7,Fare making the best of things in a
OL,8,Fnearby bedsit. Susanna says her social
OL,9,Fanxiety has worsened since the
OL,10,Fevacuation, and she has had to take
OL,11,Fsome time off work.
OL,13,FProhibition order
OL,15,FLast Friday evening, exactly four
OL,16,Fweeks after the first evacuation, the
OL,17,Fcrisis intensified.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/12
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
