PN,43307
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F433A1776946268
OL,3,CThe far-reaching impact of Plymouth's
OL,4,C'unsafe building' crisis
OL,6,FPlymouth City Council and the fire
OL,7,Fservice placed a 'prohibition order'
OL,8,Fon the building, effectively placing
OL,9,Fit on lockdown, and ordered people
OL,10,Fliving nearby to evacuate.
OL,12,FThis included Morgan Rees and his wife
OL,13,FLibby, who run a photography business
OL,14,Ftogether. They spent two nights in a
OL,15,Fhotel, then moved in with a family
OL,16,Fmember.
OL,18,FMorgan told me he is suffering from
OL,19,Fsevere facial acne, brought on by
OL,20,Fstress and lack of sleep.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/12
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
