FL,434,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43308
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F433A1776946268
OL,3,CThe far-reaching impact of Plymouth's
OL,4,C'unsafe building' crisis
OL,6,F"We haven't been told why we've been
OL,7,Fevacuated, we haven't been told how
OL,8,Flong we're going to be out for, or
OL,9,Fwhen we're going to be allowed back
OL,10,Fin", he said.
OL,12,FBusinesses count the cost
OL,14,FThe ramifications were clear to see.
OL,15,FRoads around the building were closed,
OL,16,Ftemporary traffic lights erected,
OL,17,Fresulting in traffic chaos.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/12
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
