PN,43309
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F433A1776946268
OL,3,CThe far-reaching impact of Plymouth's
OL,4,C'unsafe building' crisis
OL,6,FDurnford Street is a busy cut-through
OL,7,Ffor locals and visitors looking to
OL,8,Faccess Royal William Yard, Devil's
OL,9,FPoint and the city's ferry ports.
OL,11,FBusinesses in the yard told me they
OL,12,Ffeel cut off and forgotten, and are
OL,13,Furging the authorities to think
OL,14,Fcarefully about how they proceed.
OL,16,FTanya Marsland, who runs a bistro in
OL,17,FAdmiralty Street with her husband
OL,18,FRyan, said the hospitality industry
OL,19,Fhas taken a lot of knocks in recent
OL,20,Fyears and this feels like 'another
OL,21,Fhurdle to jump over'.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/12
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
