PN,43310
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F433A1776946268
OL,3,CThe far-reaching impact of Plymouth's
OL,4,C'unsafe building' crisis
OL,6,FA strange and frustrating crisis
OL,8,FGrey GR says it is carrying out
OL,9,Fsurveys, monitoring the situation and
OL,10,Fhoping people will be able to return
OL,11,Fhome by the end of May.
OL,13,FA spokesman said: 'We are aware of how
OL,14,Fdistressing this situation is and have
OL,15,Foffered multiple one-to-one sessions
OL,16,Fwith the property management team to
OL,17,Fanswer any concerns, while a
OL,18,Fdesignated telephone hotline and email
OL,19,Faddress remain open and active to
OL,20,Frespond to further queries.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G10/12
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,434,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43311
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F433A1776946268
OL,3,CThe far-reaching impact of Plymouth's
OL,4,C'unsafe building' crisis
OL,6,F"We know how difficult this process
OL,7,Fhas been and that some residents have
OL,8,Furgent personal concerns, and we
OL,9,Fcontinue to work as closely as
OL,10,Fpossible with these residents to
OL,11,Fensure they are safe and their
OL,12,Fwellbeing prioritised."
OL,14,FPlymouth City Council has apologised
OL,15,Ffor the disruption and promised to
OL,16,Fimprove how it communicates with those
OL,17,Faffected.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G11/12
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
