PN,43312
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F433A1776946268
OL,3,CThe far-reaching impact of Plymouth's
OL,4,C'unsafe building' crisis
OL,6,FThe situation at Evolution Cove is a
OL,7,Fstrange and frustrating crisis. It
OL,8,Fbegan with something unseen and still
OL,9,Fnot fully understood, and is spreading
OL,10,Fout exponentially beyond its origins.
OL,12,FIt is serving to highlight the
OL,13,Fprecarious nature of our housing
OL,14,Fsystem; the importance of
OL,15,Fcommunication; the dangers of
OL,16,Fmisinformation; and how a single crack
OL,17,Fcan turn so many lives upside down.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G12/12
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
